thread.title: M Keck of Lansing
thread.title_full: BookIt.com reviewed by M Keck of Lansing

author: M Keck of Lansing
title: M Keck of Lansing
text:
Had ants in our room everywhere crawling everywhere
They had a huge party in the main area not even 20 ft from our door my kids where up all night long because of the huge party going on it was about 1 am before it was quiet and my 2 four year olds didn't get much sleep
And they offered no apology or compensation for the ants or the loud party we will not likely stay there again
